Steps in packages

1) select applicable packages from the list. 
2) show the list of pakcages as per their package type.
3) display the package details for only selected packages above
4) editable values will be in input fields. whenever value edits, you must setState the value.
5) on submit, entire packages master values of selected packages and changes above, will be submitted in contracts collection in the same array format. 